TLC have one hell of a story to tell. Now for the first time their story is being told in a new VH1 film Crazy Sexy Cool: The TLC story.

The original line-up consisted of singer Tionne 'T-Boz' Watkins, rapper Lisa 'Left Eye' Lopes and singer Rozonda 'Chilli' Thomas with the group's success peaking in the 1990s.

And on Tuesday night the Tionne and Rozonda reunited on the red carpet with the actresses playing them for the premiere of the film.

