Tragically
Lisa 'Left Eye' Lopes died in a car accident in Honduras with the 
remaining two members continuing chart success without her.

Seven months later after Lisa's death 
T-Boz and Chilli released the group's fourth album 3D, which sold 2 
million copies worldwide.

The two remaining members of TLC went on to work with again Missy Elliot, featuring on the track Can You Hear Me which was on her 202 album Under Construction.

